3817  size_t Offset, size_t Size, pi_uint32 NumEventsInWaitList,
3818  const pi_event *EventsWaitList, pi_event *OutEvent, void **RetMap) {
3819  // TODO: we don't implement read-only or write-only, always read-write.
3820  // assert((map_flags & PI_MAP_READ) != 0);
3821  // assert((map_flags & PI_MAP_WRITE) != 0);
3822  PI_ASSERT(Mem, PI_ERROR_INVALID_MEM_OBJECT);
3823  PI_ASSERT(Queue, PI_ERROR_INVALID_QUEUE);
3824 
3825  ur_queue_handle_t UrQueue = reinterpret_cast<ur_queue_handle_t>(Queue);
3826  ur_mem_handle_t UrMem = reinterpret_cast<ur_mem_handle_t>(Mem);
3827 
3828  ur_map_flags_t UrMapFlags{};
3829  if (MapFlags & PI_MAP_READ)
3830  UrMapFlags |= UR_MAP_FLAG_READ;
3831  if (MapFlags & PI_MAP_WRITE)
3832  UrMapFlags |= UR_MAP_FLAG_WRITE;
3833  if (MapFlags & PI_MAP_WRITE_INVALIDATE_REGION)
3834  UrMapFlags |= UR_MAP_FLAG_WRITE_INVALIDATE_REGION;
3835 
3836  const ur_event_handle_t *UrEventsWaitList =
3837  reinterpret_cast<const ur_event_handle_t *>(EventsWaitList);
3838 
3839  ur_event_handle_t *UREvent = reinterpret_cast<ur_event_handle_t *>(OutEvent);
3840 
3841  HANDLE_ERRORS(urEnqueueMemBufferMap(UrQueue, UrMem, BlockingMap, UrMapFlags,
3842  Offset, Size, NumEventsInWaitList,
3843  UrEventsWaitList, UREvent, RetMap));
3844 
3845  return PI_SUCCESS;
3846 }

4179  auto phEvent = reinterpret_cast<ur_event_handle_t *>(event);
4180 
4181  HANDLE_ERRORS(urEnqueueWriteHostPipe(hQueue, hProgram, pipe_symbol, blocking,
4182  ptr, size, num_events_in_waitlist,
4183  phEventWaitList, phEvent));
4184

4186 }

4206 inline pi_result piEventGetInfo(pi_event Event, pi_event_info ParamName,
4207  size_t ParamValueSize, void *ParamValue,
4208  size_t *ParamValueSizeRet) {
4209 
4210  PI_ASSERT(Event, PI_ERROR_INVALID_EVENT);
4211 
4212  ur_event_handle_t UREvent = reinterpret_cast<ur_event_handle_t>(Event);
4213 
4214  ur_event_info_t PropName{};
4215  if (ParamName == PI_EVENT_INFO_COMMAND_QUEUE) {
4216  PropName = UR_EVENT_INFO_COMMAND_QUEUE;
4217  } else if (ParamName == PI_EVENT_INFO_CONTEXT) {
4218  PropName = UR_EVENT_INFO_CONTEXT;
4219  } else if (ParamName == PI_EVENT_INFO_COMMAND_TYPE) {
4220  PropName = UR_EVENT_INFO_COMMAND_TYPE;
4221  } else if (ParamName == PI_EVENT_INFO_COMMAND_EXECUTION_STATUS) {
4222  PropName = UR_EVENT_INFO_COMMAND_EXECUTION_STATUS;
4223  } else if (ParamName == PI_EVENT_INFO_REFERENCE_COUNT) {
4224  PropName = UR_EVENT_INFO_REFERENCE_COUNT;
4225  } else {
4226  return PI_ERROR_INVALID_VALUE;
4227  }
4228 
4229  HANDLE_ERRORS(urEventGetInfo(UREvent, PropName, ParamValueSize, ParamValue,
4230  ParamValueSizeRet));
4231 
4232  return PI_SUCCESS;
4233 }

4369 // Sampler
4370 inline pi_result piSamplerCreate(pi_context Context,
4371  const pi_sampler_properties *SamplerProperties,
4372  pi_sampler *RetSampler) {
4373 
4374  PI_ASSERT(Context, PI_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
4375  PI_ASSERT(RetSampler, PI_ERROR_INVALID_VALUE);
4376 
4377  ur_context_handle_t UrContext =
4378  reinterpret_cast<ur_context_handle_t>(Context);
4379  ur_sampler_desc_t UrProps{};
4380  UrProps.stype = UR_STRUCTURE_TYPE_SAMPLER_DESC;
4381 
4382  const pi_sampler_properties *CurProperty = SamplerProperties;
4383  while (*CurProperty != 0) {
4384  switch (*CurProperty) {
4385  case PI_SAMPLER_PROPERTIES_NORMALIZED_COORDS: {
4386  UrProps.normalizedCoords = ur_cast<pi_bool>(*(++CurProperty));
4387  } break;
4388 
4389  case PI_SAMPLER_PROPERTIES_ADDRESSING_MODE: {
4390  pi_sampler_addressing_mode CurValueAddressingMode =
4391  ur_cast<pi_sampler_addressing_mode>(
4392  ur_cast<pi_uint32>(*(++CurProperty)));
4393 
4394  if (CurValueAddressingMode == PI_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_MIRRORED_REPEAT)
4395  UrProps.addressingMode = UR_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_MIRRORED_REPEAT;
4396  else if (CurValueAddressingMode == PI_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_REPEAT)
4397  UrProps.addressingMode = UR_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_REPEAT;
4398  else if (CurValueAddressingMode ==
4399  PI_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_CLAMP_TO_EDGE)
4400  UrProps.addressingMode = UR_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_CLAMP_TO_EDGE;
4401  else if (CurValueAddressingMode == PI_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_CLAMP)
4402  UrProps.addressingMode = UR_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_CLAMP;
4403  else if (CurValueAddressingMode == PI_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_NONE)
4404  UrProps.addressingMode = UR_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_NONE;
4405  } break;
4406 
4407  case PI_SAMPLER_PROPERTIES_FILTER_MODE: {
4408  pi_sampler_filter_mode CurValueFilterMode =
4409  ur_cast<pi_sampler_filter_mode>(ur_cast<pi_uint32>(*(++CurProperty)));
4410 
4411  if (CurValueFilterMode == PI_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_NEAREST)
4412  UrProps.filterMode = UR_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_NEAREST;
4413  else if (CurValueFilterMode == PI_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_LINEAR)
4414  UrProps.filterMode = UR_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_LINEAR;
4415  } break;
4416 
4417  default:
4418  break;
4419  }
4420  CurProperty++;
4421  }
4422 
4423  ur_sampler_handle_t *UrSampler =
4424  reinterpret_cast<ur_sampler_handle_t *>(RetSampler);
4425 
4426  HANDLE_ERRORS(urSamplerCreate(UrContext, &UrProps, UrSampler));
4427 
4428  return PI_SUCCESS;
4429 }
4430 
4431 inline pi_result piSamplerGetInfo(pi_sampler Sampler, pi_sampler_info ParamName,
4432  size_t ParamValueSize, void *ParamValue,
4433  size_t *ParamValueSizeRet) {
4434  ur_sampler_info_t InfoType{};
4435  switch (ParamName) {
4436  case PI_SAMPLER_INFO_REFERENCE_COUNT:
4437  InfoType = UR_SAMPLER_INFO_REFERENCE_COUNT;
4438  break;
4439  case PI_SAMPLER_INFO_CONTEXT:
4440  InfoType = UR_SAMPLER_INFO_CONTEXT;
4441  break;
4442  case PI_SAMPLER_INFO_NORMALIZED_COORDS:
4443  InfoType = UR_SAMPLER_INFO_NORMALIZED_COORDS;
4444  break;
4445  case PI_SAMPLER_INFO_ADDRESSING_MODE:
4446  InfoType = UR_SAMPLER_INFO_ADDRESSING_MODE;
4447  break;
4448  case PI_SAMPLER_INFO_FILTER_MODE:
4449  InfoType = UR_SAMPLER_INFO_FILTER_MODE;
4450  break;
4451  default:
4452  return PI_ERROR_UNKNOWN;
4453  }
4454 
4455  size_t UrParamValueSizeRet;
4456  auto hSampler = reinterpret_cast<ur_sampler_handle_t>(Sampler);
4457  HANDLE_ERRORS(urSamplerGetInfo(hSampler, InfoType, ParamValueSize, ParamValue,
4458  &UrParamValueSizeRet));
4459  if (ParamValueSizeRet) {
4460  *ParamValueSizeRet = UrParamValueSizeRet;
4461  }
4462  ur2piSamplerInfoValue(InfoType, ParamValueSize, &ParamValueSize, ParamValue);
4463  fixupInfoValueTypes(UrParamValueSizeRet, ParamValueSizeRet, ParamValueSize,
4464  ParamValue);
4465  return PI_SUCCESS;
4466 }

4787 inline pi_result piextCommandBufferAdviseUSM(
4788  pi_ext_command_buffer CommandBuffer, const void *Ptr, size_t Length,
4789  pi_mem_advice Advice, pi_uint32 NumSyncPointsInWaitList,
4790  const pi_ext_sync_point *SyncPointWaitList, pi_ext_sync_point *SyncPoint) {
4791 
4792  ur_exp_command_buffer_handle_t UrCommandBuffer =
4793  reinterpret_cast<ur_exp_command_buffer_handle_t>(CommandBuffer);
4794 
4795  ur_usm_advice_flags_t UrAdvice{};
4796  if (Advice & PI_MEM_ADVICE_CUDA_SET_READ_MOSTLY) {
4797  UrAdvice |= UR_USM_ADVICE_FLAG_SET_READ_MOSTLY;
4798  }
4799  if (Advice & PI_MEM_ADVICE_CUDA_UNSET_READ_MOSTLY) {
4800  UrAdvice |= UR_USM_ADVICE_FLAG_CLEAR_READ_MOSTLY;
4801  }
4802  if (Advice & PI_MEM_ADVICE_CUDA_SET_PREFERRED_LOCATION) {
4803  UrAdvice |= UR_USM_ADVICE_FLAG_SET_PREFERRED_LOCATION;
4804  }
4805  if (Advice & PI_MEM_ADVICE_CUDA_UNSET_PREFERRED_LOCATION) {
4806  UrAdvice |= UR_USM_ADVICE_FLAG_CLEAR_PREFERRED_LOCATION;
4807  }
4808  if (Advice & PI_MEM_ADVICE_CUDA_SET_ACCESSED_BY) {
4809  UrAdvice |= UR_USM_ADVICE_FLAG_SET_ACCESSED_BY_DEVICE;
4810  }
4811  if (Advice & PI_MEM_ADVICE_CUDA_UNSET_ACCESSED_BY) {
4812  UrAdvice |= UR_USM_ADVICE_FLAG_CLEAR_ACCESSED_BY_DEVICE;
4813  }
4814  if (Advice & PI_MEM_ADVICE_CUDA_SET_ACCESSED_BY_HOST) {
4815  UrAdvice |= UR_USM_ADVICE_FLAG_SET_ACCESSED_BY_HOST;
4816  }
4817  if (Advice & PI_MEM_ADVICE_CUDA_UNSET_ACCESSED_BY_HOST) {
4818  UrAdvice |= UR_USM_ADVICE_FLAG_CLEAR_ACCESSED_BY_HOST;
4819  }
4820  if (Advice & PI_MEM_ADVICE_RESET) {
4821  UrAdvice |= UR_USM_ADVICE_FLAG_DEFAULT;
4822  }
4823 
4824  HANDLE_ERRORS(urCommandBufferAppendUSMAdviseExp(
4825  UrCommandBuffer, Ptr, Length, UrAdvice, NumSyncPointsInWaitList,
4826  SyncPointWaitList, SyncPoint));
4827  return PI_SUCCESS;
4828 }

4850 inline pi_result piextCommandBufferUpdateKernelLaunch(
4851  pi_ext_command_buffer_command command,
4852  pi_ext_command_buffer_update_kernel_launch_desc *desc) {
4853  ur_exp_command_buffer_command_handle_t UrCommand =
4854  reinterpret_cast<ur_exp_command_buffer_command_handle_t>(command);
4855  ur_exp_command_buffer_update_kernel_launch_desc_t UrDesc;
4856 
4857  UrDesc.stype = ur_structure_type_t::
4858  UR_STRUCTURE_TYPE_EXP_COMMAND_BUFFER_UPDATE_KERNEL_LAUNCH_DESC;
4859  UrDesc.numNewMemObjArgs = desc->num_mem_obj_args;
4860  UrDesc.numNewPointerArgs = desc->num_ptr_args;
4861  UrDesc.numNewValueArgs = desc->num_value_args;
4862  UrDesc.newWorkDim = desc->num_work_dim;
4863 
4864  // Convert arg descs
4865  std::vector<ur_exp_command_buffer_update_memobj_arg_desc_t> UrMemObjDescs;
4866  std::vector<ur_exp_command_buffer_update_pointer_arg_desc_t> UrPointerDescs;
4867  std::vector<ur_exp_command_buffer_update_value_arg_desc_t> UrValueDescs;
4868 
4869  for (size_t i = 0; i < UrDesc.numNewMemObjArgs; i++) {
4870  auto &PiDesc = desc->mem_obj_arg_list[i];
4871  UrMemObjDescs.push_back(
4872  {ur_structure_type_t::
4873  UR_STRUCTURE_TYPE_EXP_COMMAND_BUFFER_UPDATE_MEMOBJ_ARG_DESC,
4874  nullptr, PiDesc.arg_index, nullptr,
4875  reinterpret_cast<ur_mem_handle_t>(PiDesc.new_mem_obj)});
4876  }
4877  UrDesc.pNewMemObjArgList = UrMemObjDescs.data();
4878 
4879  for (size_t i = 0; i < UrDesc.numNewPointerArgs; i++) {
4880  auto &PiDesc = desc->ptr_arg_list[i];
4881  UrPointerDescs.push_back(
4882  {ur_structure_type_t::
4883  UR_STRUCTURE_TYPE_EXP_COMMAND_BUFFER_UPDATE_POINTER_ARG_DESC,
4884  nullptr, PiDesc.arg_index, nullptr, PiDesc.new_ptr});
4885  }
4886  UrDesc.pNewPointerArgList = UrPointerDescs.data();
4887 
4888  for (size_t i = 0; i < UrDesc.numNewValueArgs; i++) {
4889  auto &PiDesc = desc->value_arg_list[i];
4890  UrValueDescs.push_back(
4891  {ur_structure_type_t::
4892  UR_STRUCTURE_TYPE_EXP_COMMAND_BUFFER_UPDATE_VALUE_ARG_DESC,
4893  nullptr, PiDesc.arg_index, PiDesc.arg_size, nullptr,
4894  PiDesc.new_value});
4895  }
4896  UrDesc.pNewValueArgList = UrValueDescs.data();
4897 
4898  UrDesc.pNewGlobalWorkSize = desc->global_work_size;
4899  UrDesc.pNewGlobalWorkOffset = desc->global_work_offset;
4900  UrDesc.pNewLocalWorkSize = desc->local_work_size;
4901 
4902  HANDLE_ERRORS(urCommandBufferUpdateKernelLaunchExp(UrCommand, &UrDesc));
4903 
4904  return PI_SUCCESS;
4905 }

5063 inline pi_result piextBindlessImageSamplerCreate(
5064  pi_context Context, const pi_sampler_properties *SamplerProperties,
5065  float MinMipmapLevelClamp, float MaxMipmapLevelClamp, float MaxAnisotropy,
5066  pi_sampler *RetSampler) {
5067 
5068  PI_ASSERT(Context, PI_ERROR_INVALID_CONTEXT);
5069  PI_ASSERT(RetSampler, PI_ERROR_INVALID_VALUE);
5070 
5071  auto UrContext = reinterpret_cast<ur_context_handle_t>(Context);
5072  ur_sampler_desc_t UrProps{};
5073  UrProps.stype = UR_STRUCTURE_TYPE_SAMPLER_DESC;
5074 
5075  ur_exp_sampler_mip_properties_t UrMipProps{};
5076  UrMipProps.stype = UR_STRUCTURE_TYPE_EXP_SAMPLER_MIP_PROPERTIES;
5077  UrMipProps.minMipmapLevelClamp = MinMipmapLevelClamp;
5078  UrMipProps.maxMipmapLevelClamp = MaxMipmapLevelClamp;
5079  UrMipProps.maxAnisotropy = MaxAnisotropy;
5080  UrProps.pNext = &UrMipProps;
5081 
5082  ur_exp_sampler_addr_modes_t UrAddrModes{};
5083  UrAddrModes.stype = UR_STRUCTURE_TYPE_EXP_SAMPLER_ADDR_MODES;
5084  UrMipProps.pNext = &UrAddrModes;
5085  int addrIndex = 0;
5086 
5087  ur_exp_sampler_cubemap_properties_t UrCubemapProps{};
5088  UrCubemapProps.stype = UR_STRUCTURE_TYPE_EXP_SAMPLER_CUBEMAP_PROPERTIES;
5089  UrAddrModes.pNext = &UrCubemapProps;
5090 
5091  const pi_sampler_properties *CurProperty = SamplerProperties;
5092  while (*CurProperty != 0) {
5093  switch (*CurProperty) {
5094  case PI_SAMPLER_PROPERTIES_NORMALIZED_COORDS: {
5095  UrProps.normalizedCoords = ur_cast<pi_bool>(*(++CurProperty));
5096  } break;
5097 
5098  case PI_SAMPLER_PROPERTIES_ADDRESSING_MODE: {
5099  pi_sampler_addressing_mode CurValueAddressingMode =
5100  ur_cast<pi_sampler_addressing_mode>(
5101  ur_cast<pi_uint32>(*(++CurProperty)));
5102 
5103  if (CurValueAddressingMode ==
5104  PI_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_MIRRORED_REPEAT) {
5105  UrAddrModes.addrModes[addrIndex] =
5106  UR_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_MIRRORED_REPEAT;
5107  } else if (CurValueAddressingMode == PI_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_REPEAT) {
5108  UrAddrModes.addrModes[addrIndex] = UR_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_REPEAT;
5109  } else if (CurValueAddressingMode ==
5110  PI_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_CLAMP_TO_EDGE) {
5111  UrAddrModes.addrModes[addrIndex] =
5112  UR_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_CLAMP_TO_EDGE;
5113  } else if (CurValueAddressingMode == PI_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_CLAMP) {
5114  UrAddrModes.addrModes[addrIndex] = UR_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_CLAMP;
5115  } else if (CurValueAddressingMode == PI_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_NONE) {
5116  UrAddrModes.addrModes[addrIndex] = UR_SAMPLER_ADDRESSING_MODE_NONE;
5117  }
5118  addrIndex++;
5119  } break;
5120 
5121  case PI_SAMPLER_PROPERTIES_FILTER_MODE: {
5122  pi_sampler_filter_mode CurValueFilterMode =
5123  ur_cast<pi_sampler_filter_mode>(ur_cast<pi_uint32>(*(++CurProperty)));
5124 
5125  if (CurValueFilterMode == PI_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_NEAREST)
5126  UrProps.filterMode = UR_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_NEAREST;
5127  else if (CurValueFilterMode == PI_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_LINEAR)
5128  UrProps.filterMode = UR_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_LINEAR;
5129  } break;
5130 
5131  case PI_SAMPLER_PROPERTIES_MIP_FILTER_MODE: {
5132  pi_sampler_filter_mode CurValueFilterMode =
5133  ur_cast<pi_sampler_filter_mode>(ur_cast<pi_uint32>(*(++CurProperty)));
5134 
5135  if (CurValueFilterMode == PI_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_NEAREST)
5136  UrMipProps.mipFilterMode = UR_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_NEAREST;
5137  else if (CurValueFilterMode == PI_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_LINEAR)
5138  UrMipProps.mipFilterMode = UR_SAMPLER_FILTER_MODE_LINEAR;
5139  } break;
5140 
5141  case PI_SAMPLER_PROPERTIES_CUBEMAP_FILTER_MODE: {
5142  pi_sampler_cubemap_filter_mode CurValueFilterMode =
5143  ur_cast<pi_sampler_cubemap_filter_mode>(
5144  ur_cast<pi_uint32>(*(++CurProperty)));
5145 
5146  if (CurValueFilterMode == PI_SAMPLER_CUBEMAP_FILTER_MODE_SEAMLESS)
5147  UrCubemapProps.cubemapFilterMode =
5148  UR_EXP_SAMPLER_CUBEMAP_FILTER_MODE_SEAMLESS;
5149  else if (CurValueFilterMode == PI_SAMPLER_CUBEMAP_FILTER_MODE_DISJOINTED)
5150  UrCubemapProps.cubemapFilterMode =
5151  UR_EXP_SAMPLER_CUBEMAP_FILTER_MODE_DISJOINTED;
5152 
5153  } break;
5154 
5155  default:
5156  break;
5157  }
5158  CurProperty++;
5159  }
5160  UrProps.addressingMode = UrAddrModes.addrModes[0];
5161 
5162  ur_sampler_handle_t *UrSampler =
5163  reinterpret_cast<ur_sampler_handle_t *>(RetSampler);
5164 
5165  HANDLE_ERRORS(urSamplerCreate(UrContext, &UrProps, UrSampler));
5166 
5167  return PI_SUCCESS;
5168 }

5221 static void pi2urImageCopyFlags(const pi_image_copy_flags PiFlags,
5222  ur_exp_image_copy_flags_t *UrFlags) {
5223  switch (PiFlags) {
5224  case PI_IMAGE_COPY_HOST_TO_DEVICE:
5225  *UrFlags = UR_EXP_IMAGE_COPY_FLAG_HOST_TO_DEVICE;
5226  break;
5227  case PI_IMAGE_COPY_DEVICE_TO_HOST:
5228  *UrFlags = UR_EXP_IMAGE_COPY_FLAG_DEVICE_TO_HOST;
5229  break;
5230  case PI_IMAGE_COPY_DEVICE_TO_DEVICE:
5231  *UrFlags = UR_EXP_IMAGE_COPY_FLAG_DEVICE_TO_DEVICE;
5232  break;
5233  default:
5234  die("pi2urImageCopyFlags: Unsupported use case");
5235  }
5236 }

5312 static void pi2urImageInfoFlags(const pi_image_info PiFlags,
5313  ur_image_info_t *UrFlags) {
5314  switch (PiFlags) {
5315 #define PI_TO_UR_IMAGE_INFO(FROM, TO) \
5316  case FROM: { \
5317  *UrFlags = TO; \
5318  return; \
5319  }
5320  PI_TO_UR_IMAGE_INFO(PI_IMAGE_INFO_FORMAT, UR_IMAGE_INFO_FORMAT)
5321  PI_TO_UR_IMAGE_INFO(PI_IMAGE_INFO_ELEMENT_SIZE, UR_IMAGE_INFO_ELEMENT_SIZE)
5322  PI_TO_UR_IMAGE_INFO(PI_IMAGE_INFO_ROW_PITCH, UR_IMAGE_INFO_ROW_PITCH)
5323  PI_TO_UR_IMAGE_INFO(PI_IMAGE_INFO_SLICE_PITCH, UR_IMAGE_INFO_SLICE_PITCH)
5324  PI_TO_UR_IMAGE_INFO(PI_IMAGE_INFO_WIDTH, UR_IMAGE_INFO_WIDTH)
5325  PI_TO_UR_IMAGE_INFO(PI_IMAGE_INFO_HEIGHT, UR_IMAGE_INFO_HEIGHT)
5326  PI_TO_UR_IMAGE_INFO(PI_IMAGE_INFO_DEPTH, UR_IMAGE_INFO_DEPTH)
5327 #undef PI_TO_UR_IMAGE_INFO
5328  default:
5329  die("pi2urImageInfoFlags: Unsupported use case");
5330  }
5331 }

5333 inline pi_result piextMemImageGetInfo(pi_image_mem_handle MemHandle,
5334  pi_image_info ParamName, void *ParamValue,
5335  size_t *ParamValueSizeRet) {
5336  auto UrMemHandle = reinterpret_cast<ur_exp_image_mem_handle_t>(MemHandle);
5337 
5338  ur_image_info_t UrParamName{};
5339  pi2urImageInfoFlags(ParamName, &UrParamName);
5340 
5341  HANDLE_ERRORS(urBindlessImagesImageGetInfoExp(UrMemHandle, UrParamName,
5342  ParamValue, ParamValueSizeRet));
5343 
5344  if (ParamName == pi_image_info::PI_IMAGE_INFO_FORMAT && ParamValue) {
5345  pi_image_format PiFormat;
5346  ur2piImageFormat(reinterpret_cast<ur_image_format_t *>(ParamValue),
5347  &PiFormat);
5348  reinterpret_cast<pi_image_format *>(ParamValue)->image_channel_data_type =
5349  PiFormat.image_channel_data_type;
5350  reinterpret_cast<pi_image_format *>(ParamValue)->image_channel_order =
5351  PiFormat.image_channel_order;
5352  if (ParamValueSizeRet) {
5353  *ParamValueSizeRet = sizeof(pi_image_format);
5354  }
5355  }
5356 
5357  return PI_SUCCESS;
5358 }
